import { Banner, Button, Image,List, Cell, IconContainer, Icon28Chat,Icon28Stats,Icon28Devices,Input, Section } from '@telegram-apps/telegram-ui';

const TON_SITE_LINK = 'https://ton.space/';

export const BannerSection = () => (
<>
<List
  style={{
    background: 'var(--tgui--secondary_bg_color)',
    padding: '40px',
    width: 500
  }}
>

  <Section
    footer="The official Telegram app is available for Android, iPhone, iPad, Windows, macOS and Linux."
    header="Personal Information"
  >
    <Input
      header="First name"
      placeholder="21 y.o. designer from San Francisco"
    />
    <Input
      header="Last name"
      placeholder="21 y.o. designer from San Francisco"
    />
  </Section>
</List>
</>
  
);
